# Admin Standards

Follow the canonical standard: **`.ai/standards/activeadmin.md`**

Key rules:
- Use a dedicated `AdminUser`; admin auth is separate from end-user auth
- Enforce authorization with a policy adapter (Pundit/CanCanCan); deny by default
- Scope every resource for multi-tenant safety; audit privileged actions
- Use `permit_params` explicitly — never permit all attributes
- Keep registrations declarative; move logic to Service Objects
- Avoid N+1 in index/show; offload heavy exports to background jobs

